---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Pete Ghiorse — AI product leader, founder, and builder.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <p class="text-(--color-primary) font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 animate-fade-up">About</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-10 animate-fade-up stagger-1">
      Building AI that <span class="gradient-text">actually helps</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed animate-fade-up stagger-2">
      <p class="text-lg">
        I'm Pete Ghiorse &mdash; a product leader and founder who builds AI products that solve real problems for real people.
      </p>

      <p>
        Currently, I split my time between two roles: <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">Senior PM for AI/ML at Capital One</strong>,
        where I lead ML-powered fraud and spend management at scale, and building
        <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">Honeydew</strong>, an AI-powered family coordination app that uses voice, text,
        and photo input to keep families organized.
      </p>

      <p>
        Before that, I co-founded <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">GiveTide</strong>, a fintech platform I grew from zero
        to a successful acquisition in 2022 over five years.
      </p>

      <div class="border-l-2 border-(--color-primary) pl-6 py-2 my-8">
        <p class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-medium italic text-lg">
          "The best AI products disappear into the workflow. You shouldn't have to think about the technology &mdash; it should just make your life easier."
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white pt-4">What I Care About</h2>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          { title: "Useful AI", desc: "Building systems that are genuinely useful, not just technically impressive" },
          { title: "Production ML", desc: "The messy reality of shipping ML that real people depend on" },
          { title: "Agentic Systems", desc: "Multi-tool orchestration and autonomous reasoning" },
          { title: "Family Tech", desc: "Making families' lives less chaotic through technology" },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141b2d] border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1">{item.title}</p>
            <p class="text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white pt-4">Background</h2>

      <p>
        I studied <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">Finance & Economics</strong> at the
        <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">University of Richmond</strong>, graduating Magna Cum Laude.
        My career has spanned fintech, AI/ML, and consumer products &mdash; always at the intersection of
        technology and real-world impact.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
